14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 1000.4, as
15 amended by Section 2, Chapter 185, O.S.L. 2023 (59 O.S. Supp. 2024,
16 Section 1000.4), is amended to read as follows:
17 A. 1. Pursuant to and in compliance with Article I of the
18 Administrative Procedures Act, the Construction Industries Board
19 shall have the power to adopt, amend, repeal, and promulgate rules
20 as may be necessary to regulate the plumbing, electrical, roofing,
21 and mechanical trades, building and construction inspectors and home
22 inspectors. All rules promulgated by the Board shall be reviewed
23 and approved as provided in subsection F of Section 308 of Title 75
24 of the Oklahoma Statutes.
